Class FeedbackDataStoreSubSystem

Object
FeedbackDataStoreSubSystem
public class FeedbackDataStoreSubSystem extends Object

A class to handle all feedback datastore operations. This class uses strategy pattern to call datastore operations.

Since:
21-11-2023
Version:
1.0

    • FeedbackDataStoreSubSystem

      public FeedbackDataStoreSubSystem()
      Calls init(). Ensure to construct the object before other systems. If future other DataStore implementations are created, reccommended to create a Factory class to create the DataStoreInterface object.
